1 SECTION 4. AMENDMENT. Section 39-04-56 of the North Dakota Century Code is
2 amended and reenacted as follows:
3 39-04-56. Altering or forging registration card - Penalty.
4 It is a class C felony for any person to:
5 1. Alter with fraudulent intent any registration card or temporary registration permit issued
6 by the department;
7 2. Forge or counterfeit any registration card or temporary registration permit purporting to
8 have been issued by the department under the provisions of this chapter;
9 3. Alter or falsify with fraudulent intent or forge any assignment of a registration card or
10 temporary registration permit; or
11 4. Use any registration card, temporary registration permit, or assignment, knowing the
12 same to have been altered, forged, or falsified.
